@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <div class="message-box">
        <h1 style="font-size: 70px; padding-top: 0px; color: black">
            Privacy Policy
        </h1>

        <p style="font-size: 24px; color: black">
            <strong>We care about your security and privacy. Your personal information is extremely important to us, and we are committed to protecting it with the highest security standards.</strong>
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 24px; color: black;">
            <strong>How We Collect and Use Your Information?</strong><br>
            We collect only the necessary information to provide you with our services. This may include your name, email address, and other information related to your use of our site and services. All the data we collect is used solely for the purpose of improving our service and maintaining our website.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 24px; color: black;">
            <strong>Data Protection</strong><br>
            We use modern technologies to protect your data. Your information is stored in encrypted databases and processed through secure communication channels. We ensure that your data will not be shared with third parties unless required by law or for the purposes of providing our service.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 24px; color: black;">
            <strong>User Rights</strong><br>
            You have the right to request access to your personal data, update it, or delete it. You can also opt-out of receiving marketing communications from us at any time.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 24px; color: black;">
            <strong>How to Contact Us?</strong><br>
            If you have any questions regarding the protection of your personal data or our privacy policy, please feel free to contact us through the contact form on the website or through the provided contact details.
        </p>

    </div>
</div>

<style>

    body {
        background: #c0cadf 
         
        
    }

    body {
        font-family: 'Architects Daughter', cursive;
    }


    .message-box {
        background-color: rgba(211, 211, 211, 0.7); /* Леко сив цвят */
        border-radius: 15px; /* Заоблени ъгли */
        padding: 40px; /* Увеличаваме padding */
        display: block; /* Променено на block за динамично разтягане */
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Сянка за по-добър контраст */
        position: absolute; /* Позволяваме на кутийката да бъде позиционирана свободно */
        top: 150px; /* Премества кутията надолу */
        left: 50%; /* Центрираме я хоризонтално */
        transform: translateX(-50%); /* Точно центриране на кутийката */
        width: 80%; /* По-подходяща ширина за различни резолюции */
        height: auto; /* Автоматично приспособяване на височината спрямо съдържанието */
        max-width: 1000px; /* Ограничаваме ширината */
        }

